text: Aleksey Solodyankin (born 14 May 1972) is a Russian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Russia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kirov, Kirov Oblast
